targets.formattedQuery: SELECT $timeSeries as t, count() FROM $table WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY t ORDER BY t
targets.query:
SELECT
    t,
    groupArray((concat('Computed TEC ', sat), nt)) AS groupArr
FROM
(
    SELECT
        (intDiv(time, (1000)) *(1000)) AS t,
        sat,
        avg(nt) nt
    FROM computed.NT final

    WHERE
        $timeFilterMs
        AND sat IN ($satellite)
        AND sigcomb = 'L1CA+$secondaryfreq'
    GROUP BY
        t,
        sat
    ORDER BY
        t,
        sat
)
GROUP BY t

ORDER BY t
targets.rawQuery:
SELECT
    t,
    groupArray((concat('Computed TEC ', sat), nt)) AS groupArr
FROM
(
    SELECT
        (intDiv(time, (1000)) *(1000)) AS t,
        sat,
        avg(nt) nt
    FROM computed.NT final

    WHERE
        "d" >= toDate(1665942398) AND "d" <= toDate(1665942478) AND time >= toUInt64(1665942398549/1000 * 1000) AND time <= toUInt64(1665942478091/1000 * 1000)
        AND sat IN ('GLONASS1')
        AND sigcomb = 'L1CA+L2P'
    GROUP BY
        t,
        sat
    ORDER BY
        t,
        sat
)
GROUP BY t

ORDER BY t
